<p>Hello <%= @user.name.presence || @user.email %>,</p>

<p>Your <%= @purpose == Auth::EmailOtpService::PURPOSE_EMAIL_VERIFICATION ? "email verification" : "account recovery" %> code is:</p>

<p style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em;"><%= @code %></p>

<p>This code expires in <%= @expires_in_minutes %> minutes.</p>

<p>If you did not request this, you can ignore this email.</p>
